Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:33.90,OP2-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}必ず君に伝える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:38.45,OP2-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}正しさは譲れないから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:41.53,OP2-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}進み続けてゆくの
